== MediaWiki 1.47.0-PRERELEASE ==

THIS IS NOT A RELEASE YET

MediaWiki 1.47 is an alpha-quality development branch, and is not recommended
for use in production.

== Upgrading notes for 1.47 ==
Don't forget to always back up your database before upgrading!

See the file UPGRADE for more detailed per-version upgrade instructions from the
oldest supported upgrading version, MediaWiki 1.35.

Some specific notes for MediaWiki 1.47 upgrades are below:

